public class WTPartPromotionNoticeConfigSpec
extends _WTPartPromotionNoticeConfigSpec
    A ConfigSpec used to filter WTParts based on their membership in a Baseline associated to a PromotionNotice.

    Use the newWTPartPromotionNoticeConfigSpec static factory method(s), not the WTPartPromotionNoticeConfigSpec constructor, to construct instances of this class. Instances must be constructed using the static factory(s), in order to ensure proper initialization of the instance.
